snippet.title: Whirlo (SNES) - Longplay (No Deaths)
snippet.description:
Originally recorded for https://www.longplays.org

Whirlo is a side-scrolling action-platform released by Namco on July 23, 1992 in Japan for the Super Famicom video game system, and in Europe and Australia later during the same year.

This game was sometimes really a torture to beat it. The death system is like I Wanna Be The Guy. But hey, this is a No Deaths Longplay.
